    Predict state estimates on ctsmrTMB.fit object.

    predict.ctsmrTMB.fit.Rd

    Predict state estimates on ctsmrTMB.fit object.

    # S3 method for ctsmrTMB.fit
predict(
  fit,
  data = NULL,
  x0 = NULL,
  p0 = NULL,
  n.step.ahead = 1,
  ode.timestep = NULL,
  return.state.dispersion = FALSE,
  covariance = FALSE,
  give.only.n.step.ahead = FALSE,
  use.simulation = FALSE,
  sim.timestep = NULL,
  returned.sim.dt = NULL,
  n.sim = 100,
  quantiles = c(0.05, 0.5, 0.95),
  return.full.simulations = FALSE
)

    Arguments

    fit

    An ctsmrTMB.fit object from calling estimate method on ctsmrTMB object.

    data

    data.frame used to predict and update the model on which fit is based.

    use.simulation

    Boolean. If TRUE simulates the stochastic model and returns quantiles. if FALSE uses and returns the solution values for the first and second order moment differential equations. Default: FALSE

    n.sim

    Integer. Number of simulations performed if use.simulation is TRUE. Default: 100

    quantiles

    The returned state distribution quantiles if use.simulation is TRUE.

    n.step

    Integer. Number of prediction steps before updating. Default: 1

    Value

    Prediction from model
